Follow everything here:
https://github.com/meetecho/janus-gateway

When you get to ./configure, use this:

./configure --enable-libsrtp2 --disable-rabbitmq --disable-mqtt --disable--nanomsg --disable-rabbitmq-event-handler --disable-mqtt-event-handler --disable-nanomsg-event-hangler --disable-gelf-event-handler --disable-plugin-sip --disable-plugin-nosip --enable-javascript-es-module --prefix=/opt/janus
